quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  22,26,"Bonang Re nehile Abrahama ‘nqalo ea ntlo e halalelang, (Re Re): “Ho se be letho leo o ka le kopanyang le ‘Na, u be u hloekise Ntlo ea Ka malebana le batla e pota-pota le hona ho ema haufi le eona `moho le ba tla khumama ba ithapalatse"
  22,27,"“U phatlalatse bosepheleli ho batho bohle: ba tla tla ho uena ba tsamaea ka maoto, ha ba bang ba tla tla ba kaletse likamele; ba tla tla ba hlaha ka likhoro tsohle"
  22,28,"Ho tla paka lintho tse nang le molemo ho bona, le ho keteKa lebitso la Allah ka Matsatsi a fanoeng holim’a makhomo ao A ba sitsitseng ka ona sebakeng sa lihlabelo. Joale, jang le be le fane ka eona ho mafutsana"
  22,29,"Ba tlohele ho qetela lits’ebeletso tse ngolileong malebana le bona, le hona ho rapela le ho potoloha Ntlo e Halalelang ea Mathomo.”"
  22,30,"Mong le mong ea hlomphang litokelo tsa bohlokoa tsa Allah, seo se molemo ho eena kapel’a Mong`a hae. Makhomo a molemo ho lona ele lijo nakong ea bosepheleli kantle le seo le kileng la se joetsoa. Kahoo, qobang lits’ila tsa bahedene le mashano"
  22,31,"Le be le ‘nete tumelong ea Allah, le se mo kopanye le batlatsetsi; hobane ea kopanyang Allah le batlatsetsi, o ts’oana leha e ka o ile a theoha marung, eaba o hlothoa ke linonyana, kapa a fefoloa ke moea ho mo lahlela sebakeng se hole-hole"
  22,32,"Seo: Mong le mong ea ikitlaetsang ho hlompha lits’upiso tsa Allah, ka ho etsa mahlabelo a liphoofolo Ruri seo se tsoa khalalelong ea lipelo"
  22,33,Mahlabelo ao a molemo ho lona sebakeng sa pallo; mathethong sebaka sa tsona lihlabelo tseo se thoko le Ka’ba